# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copyrighted dumps — NEVER commit. These are Nintendo's BIOS/firmware images
# and the per-machine key; the build hash-verifies the owner's own dumps.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bios/*.rom
bios/*.bin
bios/*.ROM
bios/*.cfg
# (kept: bios/*.toml curated configs, bios/README.md)

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Derived-from-BIOS artifacts — recompiled BIOS C and Ghidra-extracted analysis
# are derivative works of the copyrighted dumps; regenerated, never committed.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
generated/*
!generated/.gitkeep

# Ghidra project state holds the disassembled BIOS programs (derivative) + is
# large binary churn. Keep the scripts (ghidra/*.py, *.sh) and ghidra/README.md.
ghidra/*.gpr
ghidra/*.rep/
ghidra/*.lock
ghidra/*.lock~

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Oracle emulator clone — melonDS is GPLv3, kept out of the native build and
# vendored locally by oracle/setup-melonds.sh. The oracle shim itself lives in
# oracle/shim/ (tracked); only melonDS source edits ship as oracle/patches/*.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
third_party/

# ── Build trees ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
build-*/
build_*/
*.o
*.obj
*.exe
*.a
*.lib

# ── Runtime artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.out
*.err
*.bmp
dispatch_misses.log

# Ad-hoc framebuffer captures produced while converging against the oracle.
# Curated documentation images should use descriptive names without the
# leading underscore and may be tracked explicitly.
oracle/_*.png
oracle/_*.ppm
oracle/_*.rgb

# ── Python ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# ── Editor / OS cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.user
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
